'''Wesley''' is a small man found outside [[Zahur]]'s home in [[Nardah]], just south of the fountain. For 50 coins per item (noted items work), he will crush items that requires the use of a [[pestle and mortar]], such as [[unicorn horn]]s, [[blue dragon scale]]s, [[bird nest]]s and [[chocolate bar]]s. He can crush all items in one go, so if a player is willing to pay, you can save considerable time using him instead of crushing the items yourself.

He used to work on a big ship, exploring the world with his mother. However, he did not do very well at the fleet's training school, so he quit and moved to Nardah, where he found his true passion: crushing stuff.

